column5: Not even close to the biggest, but probably one of the fattest carp I've ever landed! Haha. What do you think? Eggs or just fat full of spring food?
Good god those things are ugly   I'm sure it put up a good fight however.   Nice job Rich.
That's a lot of corn if that's indeed food in there!
Nice fish, Saturday was the first time I have seen some activity this spring and managed to hit a decent one to start. Loads of small fish cruising around. Even saw a goldfish
That is a blob of Carp  Doesn't look like it is very good to eat.
Wow...that is a chunker for sure!  It's been a while since I targeted them...maybe I should break out the carp gear again!!
Nice fish you got there Rich!! WOW whatta pig! nice job.
Fat is where it's at!  Good capture Rich.  A great start to your season.  Just imagine what you be catchin' once they start putting on the feed bag!
Nice going Rich. What a PIG !!!
El Porko! I think Mike R is right . It is probably both. WTG!
Nice fish Rich , must have put up a fight . Great way to start the carping season ...
